 konsern med 200 ansatte og en omsetning p\u00e5 90 mill. kroner. Bygningsmassen omfatter ca. 70 000 kvm. gulvflate fordelt p\u00e5 32 eiendommer, hovedsakelig i Trondheim sentrum."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e419eae7c1972042731b96e393e3dfcf104ae744f0057cde64726cb4c1f2ea78"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-24T22:11:48.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Viking Hotel i Thomas Angells gate skifter eiere 15. juni, da det innlemmes i hotellimperiet som Realinvest AS er i ferd med \u00e5 bygge opp i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1138117.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/realinvest"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d5a5484b351a8015ac6d0902b5d3ed32d1a97fd3.jpg?597128ab"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Stor i sm\u00e5 hoteller -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "d5a5484b351a8015ac6d0902b5d3ed32d1a97fd3"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "travel"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "realinvest as"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["eid", "sm\u00e5 hoteller", "hotell"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["viking hotel", "hans hoff", "mona og hans hoff", "larsen", "hans og mona hoff", "julian o. og ragnhild w. riise", "hilde riise kojan og tor w. riise"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["thomas angells", "hilde riise kojan", "tor w. rii